---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Tentang Kami" description="Toko mandiri: beli langsung di website atau lewat marketplace pilihan Anda" canonicalUrl={Astro.url.href}>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
    <!-- JSON-LD Organization -->
    <script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Organization',
      name: 'Astro Marketplace',
      url: Astro.url.origin,
      logo: '/favicon.svg',
      sameAs: [
        'https://www.tokopedia.com/',
        'https://shopee.co.id/'
      ]
    })}</script>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700">Penjual Mandiri</span>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Belanja Mudah. Pilihan Fleksibel.</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-gray-600">
        Kami berfokus pada pengalaman belanja yang cepat, aman, dan informatif. Anda dapat
        <strong>membeli langsung</strong> dari website ini atau memilih <strong>marketplace</strong> favorit seperti Tokopedia atau Shopee.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/store" class="rounded-lg bg-emerald-600 px-4 py-2 text-white hover:bg-emerald-700">Lihat Produk</a>
        <a href="/kebijakan" class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300">Kebijakan Toko</a>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Value props -->
    <section class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="group rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200 transition hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700">âœ¨</div>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Produk Terpilih</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Kualitas terkurasi dengan deskripsi yang jelas dan foto yang informatif.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200 transition hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700">âš¡</div>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Pengiriman Cepat</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Proses 1â€“2 hari kerja, informasi resi dikirim otomatis.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200 transition hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700">ðŸ’¬</div>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Dukungan Responsif</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Tim kecil yang sigap membantu sebelum dan sesudah pembelian.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How to buy -->
    <section class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Cara Beli Langsung</h2>
        <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal space-y-2 pl-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Buka halaman <a href="/store" class="underline">Store</a> dan pilih produk</li>
          <li>Klik <span class="font-medium">Add to Cart</span> lalu lanjut ke Checkout</li>
          <li>Isi data pengiriman dan konfirmasi pesanan</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Beli via Marketplace</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">Pada halaman produk, klik tombol <em>Beli di {`{Marketplace}`}</em> untuk diarahkan ke toko resmi kami.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Catatan: untuk transaksi atau kendala di marketplace, mohon menghubungi dukungan marketplace terkait.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1">Tokopedia</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1">Shopee</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Info blocks -->
    <section class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Pengiriman & Pengembalian</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Pengiriman 1â€“2 hari kerja. Pengembalian dalam 7 hari sesuai <a class="underline" href="/kebijakan">kebijakan</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Privasi</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Kami menjaga data Anda. Baca <a class="underline" href="/privacy">kebijakan privasi</a> untuk detailnya.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="mt-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-50 to-white p-10 text-center ring-1 ring-emerald-100">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-900">Butuh bantuan untuk memilih produk?</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-emerald-800">Hubungi kami â€” kami siap membantu.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/store" class="rounded-lg bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-700">Belanja Sekarang</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 px-5 py-2.5 text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-100">Hubungi Kami</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>


